    SAM is an extensible markup language with syntax similar to Markdown but semantic capability similar to XML.

    * For a quick introduction to SAM, see {Quickstart}(link "quickstart.html").
    * For a full descripition of the language, see {Language}(link "language.html").
    * For some recipies for solving common markup issues with SAM, see {Recipes}(link "recipes.html").
    * To run the SAM parser, see {Parser}(link "parser.html").
    * To install the SAM parser, see the {Github page}(https://github.com/mbakeranalecta/sam).